1
00:00:39,960 --> 00:00:41,759
Let Wei Wei go, now!

2
00:00:41,759 --> 00:00:42,679
Dali!

3
00:00:43,039 --> 00:00:44,880
Stay out of this, kid.

4
00:00:45,719 --> 00:00:46,479
My eyes!

5
00:00:46,479 --> 00:00:47,200
Long Xiao!

6
00:00:47,200 --> 00:00:48,399
I'll kill you!

7
00:00:52,640 --> 00:00:55,000
I'm the Head of Security, after all.

8
00:00:56,119 --> 00:00:57,000
Huilian!

9
00:00:57,359 --> 00:00:58,320
What did you do to her?

10
00:00:58,920 --> 00:00:59,719
Call an ambulance!

11
00:00:59,719 --> 00:01:01,119
Hurry, come on!

12
00:01:06,319 --> 00:01:07,040
Move aside.

13
00:01:07,400 --> 00:01:08,079
Out of the way.

14
00:01:10,239 --> 00:01:11,359
Move, move!

15
00:01:15,079 --> 00:01:15,599
Doctor!

16
00:01:15,879 --> 00:01:16,719
How is she, Doc?

17
00:01:16,920 --> 00:01:17,799
Use the best medicine.

18
00:01:17,799 --> 00:01:18,760
Money's no object.

19
00:01:19,359 --> 00:01:20,319
Family, please calm down.

20
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:23,159
The patient's eye damage is irreversible.

21
00:01:23,159 --> 00:01:24,879
And she's bleeding heavily.

22
00:01:24,879 --> 00:01:26,040
She needs a transfusion immediately.

23
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:27,560
Doc, take mine.

24
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:28,519
Wei Wei and I are both Type A.

25
00:01:28,719 --> 00:01:29,480
Hurry up, please!

26
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:30,519
That's great!

27
00:01:30,760 --> 00:01:31,239
Nurse Zhang!

28
00:01:31,359 --> 00:01:31,760
Right away.

29
00:01:31,840 --> 00:01:33,120
Take them for cross-matching.

30
00:01:33,120 --> 00:01:33,799
Prepare for transfusion.

31
00:01:42,879 --> 00:01:43,480
Zhu Yihai.

32
00:01:43,920 --> 00:01:45,120
I've been telling you for ages.

33
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:46,359
The doctor said to go home and rest.

34
00:01:46,359 --> 00:01:47,640
Your wounds haven't healed yet.

35
00:01:47,640 --> 00:01:48,680
Could you just go back?

36
00:01:48,959 --> 00:01:49,719
Have some water first.

37
00:01:51,359 --> 00:01:51,920
Dahai.

38
00:01:52,239 --> 00:01:52,879
Drink some water.

39
00:01:54,959 --> 00:01:55,519
Dahai.

40
00:01:56,400 --> 00:01:57,519
The doctor told him to go home.

41
00:01:57,760 --> 00:01:58,560
But he just won't listen.

42
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:03,000
Dahai.

43
00:02:03,480 --> 00:02:04,239
Don't worry.

44
00:02:04,519 --> 00:02:05,920
The blood types are bound to match.

45
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:06,879
Stop overthinking it.

46
00:02:07,319 --> 00:02:08,159
Go home and rest first.

47
00:02:08,719 --> 00:02:09,520
If you collapse too,

48
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:10,400
what will the rest of us do?

49
00:02:14,759 --> 00:02:15,080
Let's go.

50
00:02:17,199 --> 00:02:18,439
I'll leave Wei Wei in your hands.

51
00:02:18,639 --> 00:02:19,400
Yeah, okay.

52
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:41,639
Wait here a second.

53
00:02:41,639 --> 00:02:43,000
Let me clean up your wound.

54
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,039
Does your head still hurt?

55
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:54,520
I'm fine.

56
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:00,479
Give me your hand.

57
00:03:03,759 --> 00:03:04,560
Lili.

58
00:03:07,120 --> 00:03:08,879
Do you think I did the wrong thing?

59
00:03:09,159 --> 00:03:11,120
If I hadn't been so stubborn...

60
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:12,039
Don't say that.

61
00:03:13,400 --> 00:03:14,439
None of this is your fault.

62
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,280
I know you're trying to comfort me.

63
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,879
But all of this...

64
00:03:21,879 --> 00:03:23,319
started because of me.

65
00:03:26,319 --> 00:03:27,439
Don't blame yourself.

66
00:03:29,599 --> 00:03:30,840
You shouldn't blame yourself.

67
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:32,199
How can I not blame myself?

68
00:03:33,439 --> 00:03:34,319
Because of me,

69
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:36,400
Xiong Dali almost went to prison.

70
00:03:36,400 --> 00:03:37,520
Ge Bing got kidnapped.

71
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,719
Wei Wei is still fighting for her life.

72
00:03:38,719 --> 00:03:39,759
Dahai.

73
00:03:39,759 --> 00:03:41,039
You need to pull yourself together now.

74
00:03:41,039 --> 00:03:41,800
Become stronger.

75
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:43,280
Only then can you protect them.

76
00:03:56,120 --> 00:03:56,919
Thank you.

77
00:03:59,199 --> 00:04:00,439
You've helped me so much.

78
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,879
I haven't been much help.

79
00:04:10,840 --> 00:04:12,199
But you've helped me a lot.

80
00:04:21,879 --> 00:04:23,480
I know you've forgotten a lot of things.

81
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:30,319
But do you remember why you went to jail?

82
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:32,199
Wasn't it because Long Xiao set me up?

83
00:04:32,199 --> 00:04:33,600
It had nothing to do with Long Xiao.

84
00:04:37,920 --> 00:04:40,079
You finally found the man who violated me.

85
00:04:41,959 --> 00:04:43,279
You did it to avenge me.

86
00:04:55,920 --> 00:04:57,319
Thank you, Dahai.

87
00:05:00,759 --> 00:05:02,399
Thank you for saving me.

88
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:11,839
Can you hold me?

89
00:05:31,519 --> 00:05:33,480
You're the only one who won't look down on me.

90
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:45,040
Dahai.

91
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,560
Love me.

92
00:06:09,759 --> 00:06:11,160
I love you.

93
00:06:17,439 --> 00:06:18,160
We can't.

94
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:19,480
She's my mom.

95
00:06:23,360 --> 00:06:23,879
Lili.

96
00:06:24,839 --> 00:06:26,639
Let's just go to the hospital to see Wei Wei.

97
00:06:53,879 --> 00:06:54,480
Nurse.

98
00:06:54,839 --> 00:06:55,319
Nurse.

99
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:56,480
Nurse.

100
00:06:57,439 --> 00:06:58,839
Doctor, about our blood...

101
00:06:59,279 --> 00:06:59,800
Nurse.

102
00:07:00,079 --> 00:07:01,240
What's the situation in there?

103
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:02,959
Is my blood a match?

104
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:09,959
As for the blood we need now...

105
00:07:09,959 --> 00:07:11,279
I don't know when it'll arrive.

106
00:07:11,279 --> 00:07:12,639
Dali, how is it?

107
00:07:12,639 --> 00:07:14,399
Hai, our blood types don't match.

108
00:07:14,399 --> 00:07:15,720
I've already contacted the city blood bank.

109
00:07:15,720 --> 00:07:17,199
But I don't know when it'll get here.

110
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:17,720
Okay.

111
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:18,879
Thank you, Ge Bing.

112
00:07:19,199 --> 00:07:19,800
No problem.

113
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:22,319
Doctor.

114
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,279
We're both Type A. Why doesn't it match?

115
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:25,560
I'm very sorry.

116
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:27,480
We need more than just matching blood types.

117
00:07:27,480 --> 00:07:29,160
We need cross-matching.

118
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:30,000
So...

119
00:07:30,000 --> 00:07:31,720
your blood isn't a complete match.

120
00:07:35,399 --> 00:07:36,000
Lili.

121
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,879
Aren't you Type A too?

122
00:07:42,480 --> 00:07:43,000
Lili.

123
00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:46,920
I don't know.

124
00:07:47,439 --> 00:07:48,120
Let's go get you checked.

125
00:07:49,759 --> 00:07:50,240
Fine.

126
00:07:50,759 --> 00:07:51,399
Thanks.

127
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:57,920
Lili.

128
00:07:58,959 --> 00:07:59,879
Thank you.

129
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:03,000
Nothing to thank me for.

130
00:08:04,759 --> 00:08:06,240
Wei Wei isn't just your friend.

131
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:11,920
Family of the patient.

132
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:14,519
Citizen Qiao Lili's blood test results are in.

133
00:08:14,519 --> 00:08:15,639
She has Type AB blood.

134
00:08:15,639 --> 00:08:16,839
She doesn't meet the transfusion criteria.

135
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:22,920
So she's not my mom.

136
00:08:23,319 --> 00:08:24,839
I can't help much here.

137
00:08:25,160 --> 00:08:26,680
I'll head back to the pool hall to tidy up.

138
00:08:28,759 --> 00:08:29,279
Lili.

139
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:30,000
Lili.

140
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,679
Zhu Yihai.

141
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:37,200
Why are you standing here like an idiot?

142
00:08:37,480 --> 00:08:38,200
What's wrong?

143
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:42,159
Isn't that Huilian's necklace?

144
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:43,799
Where'd you get it?

145
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:45,000
Long Xiao gave it to me.

146
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:01,120
The guest in the presidential suite,

147
00:09:01,120 --> 00:09:02,200
no one is allowed to disturb him.

148
00:09:02,919 --> 00:09:03,919
Is that clear?

149
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:06,879
Why is Long Xiao here?

150
00:09:17,639 --> 00:09:19,080
I've searched the whole Guohong Factory.

151
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:19,759
Couldn't find her.

152
00:09:21,559 --> 00:09:24,039
Where on earth could she have gone?

153
00:09:24,039 --> 00:09:25,159
Huilian is in danger because of you.

154
00:09:25,919 --> 00:09:27,399
If anything happens to her,

155
00:09:27,799 --> 00:09:28,720
I'm not done with you.

156
00:09:29,039 --> 00:09:30,200
I don't need you to tell me that.

157
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,039
I'm more worried than you are.

158
00:09:32,279 --> 00:09:33,440
Let's go straight to Long Xiao.

159
00:09:33,639 --> 00:09:34,840
Hai, let's take him down.

160
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:44,399
Jiao Jing, you've got the nerve to come here?

161
00:09:48,879 --> 00:09:49,600
Zhu Yihai.

162
00:09:50,120 --> 00:09:52,279
Look at you all, what a pathetic mess.

163
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:53,720
Spill it.

164
00:09:54,240 --> 00:09:55,639
What did Long Xiao send you here for?

165
00:09:58,159 --> 00:09:59,200
Long Xiao sent this for you.

166
00:10:00,080 --> 00:10:01,200
What's in this?

167
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,559
I don't know anything.

168
00:10:02,879 --> 00:10:03,919
I'm just a messenger.

169
00:10:19,879 --> 00:10:21,879
What kind of crap is this? So hard to use.

170
00:10:30,840 --> 00:10:31,639
Zhu Yihai.

171
00:10:32,279 --> 00:10:33,519
We meet again.

172
00:10:34,480 --> 00:10:35,840
Today,

173
00:10:35,840 --> 00:10:37,039
I went out of my way

174
00:10:37,519 --> 00:10:38,960
to bring you

175
00:10:39,639 --> 00:10:40,799
an old friend of yours.

176
00:10:47,200 --> 00:10:47,759
Come on.

177
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:50,519
Say hi to your Lover boy.

178
00:10:50,679 --> 00:10:51,639
Bastard!

179
00:10:52,639 --> 00:10:53,720
If you keep being stubborn,

180
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:55,120
and just like your little buddy,

181
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:55,799
I'll take a knife

182
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:58,240
and gouge your eyeballs out.

183
00:11:00,919 --> 00:11:01,799
Let me tell you,

184
00:11:02,120 --> 00:11:03,080
mess with me,

185
00:11:03,639 --> 00:11:05,279
and it won't end well for you.

186
00:11:06,120 --> 00:11:08,000
I'll take everyone around you,

187
00:11:08,759 --> 00:11:10,200
one by one,

188
00:11:10,720 --> 00:11:12,759
and torture them to death.

189
00:11:18,600 --> 00:11:20,799
I really had no idea it was this.

190
00:11:20,799 --> 00:11:21,559
Jiao Jing.

191
00:11:22,639 --> 00:11:23,759
Listen to me.

192
00:11:24,159 --> 00:11:26,480
You and I are in the same boat now.

193
00:11:27,159 --> 00:11:28,960
Long Xiao doesn't just want me dead.

194
00:11:29,399 --> 00:11:31,159
He wants you gone too. Get it?

195
00:11:33,279 --> 00:11:34,200
That's impossible.

196
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:36,200
A scumbag like Long Xiao

197
00:11:36,799 --> 00:11:39,480
will assume the worst about everyone.

198
00:11:39,879 --> 00:11:41,360
Just because of this videotape,

199
00:11:41,639 --> 00:11:42,559
believe it or not,

200
00:11:43,080 --> 00:11:44,879
he expects me to kill you.

201
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:53,480
Dali, open the door for her.

202
00:12:03,120 --> 00:12:05,120
You've got two choices now.

203
00:12:05,120 --> 00:12:06,759
Either help me rescue Huilian

204
00:12:06,759 --> 00:12:07,720
and take Long Xiao down,

205
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:08,759
or

206
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:10,600
you walk right out that door.

207
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:12,480
Go back to Long Xiao

208
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:13,960
and see if he doesn't eliminate you.

209
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:16,080
Do I even have a choice?

210
00:12:16,080 --> 00:12:17,120
No, you don't.

